{"tid":2385277,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東發大廈餐廳7職員被指無在指定期間檢測各被罰5千元","createTime":"2021-01-29T03:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T03:36:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c88be856037e685cd4d9b0c8e86f98a2a494b549","tid":2385277,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"北角東發大廈強制檢測行動歷時12小時，早上7時結束。<br />\n<br />\n在有關指明「受限區域」內的餐廳表示，7名職員通宵留在餐廳內，早上獲發告票，指他們無在指定期間內接受檢測，各人被罰款5000元。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名職員說，昨晚7時警方圍封現場時，要求他們留在店舖，等待通知再前往檢測，餐廳昨晚有下半閘，亦有開燈，大家輪流休息，但整晚無人通知他們要前往檢測，直至早上外出了解情況時，被指無在指定時間內接受檢測而被票控。他於是向在場人員反映昨晚情況，對方向他們表示可就罰款提交書面解釋。<br />\n<br />\n該餐廳負責人Jason說，當局並無清晰向商戶交代檢測安排，最終員工被罰款，他感到無奈。他說，餐廳今天不會營業，讓員工休息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572990-20210129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572990-20210129.htm&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w5mLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=1f4e906b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572990-20210129.htm&h=dc7ac7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572990-20210129.htm</a>"},{"pid":"554bf7a3615d1aa7195af6d31ccf4fa8e60ec867","tid":2385277,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"179583b043160892f893e1968624cb96b2dee1b0","tid":2385277,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da5e9df3912a3054dfdf02f03186d51dbb8924ac","tid":2385277,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚 害死黃店呀"},{"pid":"cfbc0c95ba462200507c92ebfd2daa5bab35c26e","tid":2385277,"uid":77196,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">對方向他們表示可就罰款提交書面解釋</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n乜撚野書面解釋